{"tid":299483,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所嚴正澄清市場傳聞(強制毫子般退市)","createTime":"2017-06-27T06:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T11:14:07.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1069b580b632753d236cd76668a20c785355ae3f","tid":299483,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:41:59.000Z","msg":"����ӥx<br />\n<br />\n�A�ȱ���<br />\n<br />\n�K�d�n��<br />\n<br />\n�p���F��<br />\n<br />\n�s�i�A��<br />\n<br />\n�p���ڭ�<br />\n<br />\nFAQ<br />\n<br />\n���v<br />\n<br />\n�[�J�ڭ�<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n即時新聞 | 本地及兩岸<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;即時新聞&nbsp;--- 本地及兩岸&nbsp;--- 國際&nbsp;--- 財經&nbsp;--- 體育&nbsp;--- 立法會道一號&nbsp;交通消息&nbsp;--- 即時交通&nbsp;--- 特別封路&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n港交所嚴正澄清市場傳聞<br />\n<br />\n27.06.2017 14:18<br />\n<br />\n今日有多隻細價股暴跌，有傳聞說是港交所(<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=rXCVhASnXJoK16ypx%2F2IBJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=436e78ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>)前天提交了提案，為激活香港小企業創新，要強制將低於1元且平時交投不活躍的僵屍股退市。港交所嚴正澄清，相關傳聞完全沒有事實根據。<br />\n<br />\n細價股午後繼續捱沽，但部份跌幅略為收窄。漢華專業服務(<a href=\"http://08193.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F08193.HK&d=rXCVhASnXJoK16ypx%2F2IBJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b741edbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">08193.HK</a>)和集成控股(<a href=\"http://01027.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01027.HK&d=rXCVhASnXJoK16ypx%2F2IBJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e087c1e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01027.HK</a>)急挫九成三，匯隆控股(<a href=\"http://08021.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F08021.HK&d=rXCVhASnXJoK16ypx%2F2IBJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a633e259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">08021.HK</a>)跌近八成半，上諭集團(<a href=\"http://01633.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01633.HK&d=rXCVhASnXJoK16ypx%2F2IBJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e7c07267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01633.HK</a>)和美捷匯(<a href=\"http://01389.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01389.HK&d=rXCVhASnXJoK16ypx%2F2IBJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=08a137b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01389.HK</a>)跌七成三至七成八。"},{"pid":"311e1b189dcf127f3fe68a2bbff7f16914057f13","tid":299483,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"細價股事件翻版?"},{"pid":"16057eda48f62d5de2c4049ab58df86a3f2542c0","tid":299483,"uid":44980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:10:21.000Z","msg":"就算真，以為d莊唔識合股交波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc6a3088803736a5689fcea34fe8a038937a2e3","tid":299483,"uid":31269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"合股，改round lot...合到過一蚊，搞掂。"},{"pid":"da399a7f2db0b7e1b88910fee1908c694b185ca6","tid":299483,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"我係fb見到有條疑似做雞被包養既女話40萬@0.7跌到得0.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戇鳩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  做雞係唔同啲"},{"pid":"8b135145713807046c2f0771e7e861d145dadcbe","tid":299483,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"信錯老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5bf4b5a112cff8d6a4c7b97511ef1ddb6a124c","tid":299483,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係fb見到有條疑似做雞被包養既女話40萬@0.7跌到得0.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 